{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1141","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":null,"news_on_top":"1","news_title":"聯合國：非洲之角乾旱惡化 1300萬人面臨饑荒","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>2022-02-08 20:36 中央社 / 奈洛比8日綜合外電報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><img alt='' src='http://www.ctspcsr.com.tw/user_files/news_files/%E9%A3%A2%E8%8D%92.JPG' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>聯合國世界糧食計劃署（WFP）今天指出，非洲之角（Horn of Africa）地區正經歷數十年來最嚴重乾旱。圖／路透社</span></span></p>\n\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;' />\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>聯合國世界糧食計劃署（WFP）今天指出，非洲之角（Horn of Africa）地區正經歷數十年來最嚴重乾旱，估計肯亞、索馬利亞及衣索比亞有1300萬人正面臨嚴重饑荒。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>世界糧食計劃署表示，非洲之角地區（非洲大陸東北沿海一帶）發生自1981年以來最嚴重乾旱，已連續3個雨季都無法解旱。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>肯亞、衣索比亞及索馬利亞有大片地區正發生乾旱，這些地區營養不良比例甚高，今年第一季約有1300萬人處於嚴重饑荒風險中，糧食援助正在這些地區分發。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>世界糧食計劃署東非地區主任鄧福德（MichaelDunford）告訴法新社，水及牧地短缺，加上預計未來幾個月降雨量將低於平均值，人們恐怕只會面臨更多苦難。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>他在聲明中指出：「乾旱屢次侵襲非洲之角，毀掉了收成，牲畜正在死去，饑荒現正加劇」。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>資料來源:&nbsp;</span><a href='https://udn.com/news/story/6812/6084344?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>https://udn.com/news/story/6812/6084344?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</span></a></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2022-02-09","clk_count":"60"}},"__N_SSG":true}